'''"Most of the world has no judicial supervision on elections, however, those elections are fair and impartial".'''<ref name="daralhayat">[http://international.daralhayat.com/internationalarticle/72415 Â«National Democratic PartyÂ» emphasizes the unity of the parliamentary majority to reap and rejects any international monitoring of the elections]</ref>|[[Gamal Mubarak]], in a press conference
